                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony2-rest/edit/master/knpu/episode1/get-collection.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Our API client will need a way to fetch a collection of programmers. Piece
of cake. Start with <code>public function listAction()</code>. For the URI, use
<code>/api/programmers</code> and add an <code>@Method("GET")</code>:</p>
