</p>
<p>So, the URI you POST to when creating a resource - <code>/api/programmers</code> -
will be the same as the one you'll GET to fetch a collection of programmer
resources. And yes, you can filter and paginate this list - all stuff we'll
do later on.</p>
<p>Inside <code>listAction()</code>, start like we always do: with a query.
<code>$programmers = $this-&gt;getDoctrine()-&gt;getRepository('AppBundle:Programmer')</code>
and for now, we'll find everything with <code>findAll()</code>:</p>
